rows.label: bf05090100_0010
rows.name:
Well then,
I should probably be the guide from here on.

rows.label: bf05090100_0020
rows.name:
We just need to go to the other side 
of the ridge, right?

rows.label: bf05090100_0030
rows.name:
Indeed. The delegation from Acedia
will meet us there.

rows.label: bf05090100_0040
rows.name: Got it!

rows.label: bf05090100_0050
rows.name:
Will leave it to boss!
Lead the way!

rows.label: bf05090100_0055
rows.name: Hehehe.

rows.label: bf05090100_0060
rows.name:
What's with the "hehehe"?
We're just following the chain of floating islands.

rows.label: bf05090100_0070
rows.name:
Depending on the route, 
it can be dangerous, right?

rows.label: bf05090100_0080
rows.name: We might be attacked by tough monsters.

rows.label: bf05090100_0090
rows.name: Well, that's certainly true...

rows.label: bf05090100_0100
rows.name: So how we going?

rows.label: bf05090100_0110
rows.name: Err...

rows.label: bf05090100_0115
rows.name: What about Iyasaki Village?

rows.label: bf05090100_0120
rows.name: Iyasaki Village?

rows.label: bf05090100_0125
rows.name: Will we pass through it?

rows.label: bf05090100_0130
rows.name: I mean, we could go that way.

rows.label: bf05090100_0135
rows.name:
That's it!
I want to go by that route.

rows.label: bf05090100_0140
rows.name: Don't be so eager.

rows.label: bf05090100_0150
rows.name: You're unusually excited, aren't you?

rows.label: bf05090100_0155
rows.name: Her objective has changed, meh.

rows.label: bf05090100_0160
rows.name: But[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf05090100_0170
rows.name: Don't you want to see Rex's hometown?

rows.label: bf05090100_0180
rows.name: Ah, I might want to see that, true.

rows.label: bf05090100_0190
rows.name:
Well, that route is relatively safe,
so it's not a bad idea[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf05090100_0200
rows.name: What do you think?

rows.label: bf05090100_0210
rows.name: I'll leave it to Rex-sama.

rows.label: bf05090100_0220
rows.name:
Then let's do it! We'll head off
as soon as we're ready!

rows.label: bf05090100_0230
rows.name: Yeah!

rows.label: bf05090100_0240
rows.name: Hey, why are you here too?

rows.label: bf05090100_0250
rows.name:
As the acting Emperor of Superbia,
I offered to accompany you.

rows.label: bf05090100_0260
rows.name: Is there a problem?

rows.label: bf05090100_0270
rows.name: No, not at all.

rows.label: bf05090100_0280
rows.name: Since the Holy See is inviting Heaven's Holy Grail,

rows.label: bf05090100_0290
rows.name: that information must be open to all countries.

rows.label: bf05090100_0300
rows.name:
So it's all about maintaining
a neutral, fair position, is that it?

rows.label: bf05090100_0310
rows.name: Yes.

rows.label: bf05090100_0320
rows.name:
That's how it is.
Please get along, Nia.

rows.label: bf05090100_0330
rows.name:
As someone who was thrown in jail,
I'm really uncomfortable, you know.

rows.label: bf05090100_0340
rows.name:
Well, please don't say that, my lady. Meleph-sama 
and Kagutsuchi-sama will be accompanying us.

rows.label: bf05090100_0350
rows.name: The safety of our journey is practically guaranteed.

rows.label: bf05090100_0360
rows.name: Well, I guess that's true, but...

rows.label: bf05090100_0370
rows.name: Come on, Nia.

rows.label: bf05090100_0380
rows.name:
The misunderstanding has been cleared up, nand they 
helped us the other day, didn't they?

rows.label: bf05090100_0390
rows.name: It's nice how blissfully clueless you are.

rows.label: bf05090100_0400
rows.name: I'm an optimist[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf05090100_0410
rows.name: You want me to call it "optimistic," right?

rows.label: bf05090100_0420
rows.name:
Fine.
Let's put it all behind us.

rows.label: bf05090100_0430
rows.name: Yeah, let's make up.

rows.label: bf05090100_0440
rows.name: I'm counting on you too.
